                     halfling has a +2 racial bonus on Jump checks because
                     halflings are agile and athletic.  If you have the
                     Acrobatic feat, you get a +2 bonus on Jump checks.";
  synergy            "If you have 5 or more ranks in Tumble, you get a +2 bonus
                     on Jump checks.  If you have 5 or more ranks in Jump, you
                     get a +2 bonus on Tumble checks.";
