                     and their special powers or vulnerabilities. In general,
                     the DC of such a check equals 10 + the monster’s HD. A
                     successful check allows you to remember a bit of useful
                     information about that monster. For every 5 points by
                     which your check result exceeds the DC, you recall another
                     piece of useful information.";
